LOADING DATABASE DUMP

Need to increase max allowed packet:

Open a terminal, type mysql to get a mysql prompt, and issue these commands:

set global net_buffer_length=1000000; 
set global max_allowed_packet=1000000000;
create database corpus;

Then in another terminal window:

mysql -h hostname -u user -p < filename


PYTHON PACKAGE DEPENDENCIES

(use easy_install)
SQLObject
MySQL-python
lxml
whoosh

pyLucene:
In JCC dir:
python setup.py build
sudo python setup.py install
And then cd ..
vi Makefile: make necessary changes
make; make install
